        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1361316168" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1884451074994290641">Another masterpiece by Naguib Mahfouz,mixture of fantasy, and Egyptian melodrama, short stories combined to make a complete, connected novel. I wish to see a movie out of this book.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


