      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/5835922.Naguib_Mahfouz">About Naguib Mahfouz</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/5835922.Naguib_Mahfouz"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1448319849p3/5835922.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/5835922.Naguib_Mahfouz">Naguib Mahfouz
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
13,719
followers
</div>

